## Changes (`src/context.rs`)

**Added `ensure_embedding_index()` function** (lines 369–402) that mirrors the `ensure_semantic_index()` pattern:
• Checks if `.yoyo/context-embedding-index.json` exists
• If valid and fresh: returns early (no-op)
• If stale: removes the file and prints a yellow diagnostic
• If corrupt/schema-mismatched: removes the file and prints a yellow diagnostic
• If missing: prints a one-line yellow diagnostic: `"embedding index is missing — embedding-based context ranking is unavailable (requires an external embedding model)"`

**Called from `build_deepseek_context_preview()`** (line 410) immediately after `ensure_semantic_index()`, turning the previously silent "missing" into an observable diagnostic.

